    public static class EntityPropertyComparators.Ordered
extends LinkedHashMap<String,Integer>
implements Comparator<EntityPropertyDescriptor>
    Comparator that contains a map of property names with a specified order. Undefined properties are assumed to have an order index of Ordered.LOWEST_PRECEDENCE.
